{
  "stem": "14897.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he went up a tree and spent the night in the trees hiding from the wolves.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the soldiers probably didn't march at night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But anyway, he joined us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And life in that little town-- the town had a considerable Jewish population, did not have any doctors who were not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the Germans divided the doctors, the Jewish doctors, into the those who could only treat the Jews and those who could only treat the Poles.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father was one of the doctors who was only allowed to treat the Poles.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father was very street-smart.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had lived through the Russian Revolution.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He hated the Russians, as you understand from his political views, which were probably very much shaped by, by his fate, by his story doing the Russian Revolution.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he felt that living in a small town, Jews, where we didn't have really close friends except other refugees, that we were very exposed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He felt that we would have a better chance if we actually went back to the ghetto of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So the decision was made to try to make it to the ghetto of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was also very brave, as I realized later on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, you know, I'm going to go to the Gestapo and ask for a pass to go back home to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he went with my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now that I think of it, as an adult, I think it was a very rash decision to leave me alone, and the two of them going to Gestapo might never have come back.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My mother, I could understand it.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
